long_description: Spacious and bright apartment in a quiet area of Prague 6. The apartment features a modern kitchen, renovated bathroom, and large balcony with garden views.
Newly renovated studio apartment in the heart of Prague 1. Perfect for young professionals or as an investment property. Fully furnished with high-end appliances.
Stunning apartment with panoramic views of Prague Castle. Features high ceilings, original hardwood floors, and a newly installed designer kitchen. Private parking included.
Charming apartment in a historic building. Recently renovated with preserved period features. Excellent location near Náměstí Míru.
Spacious family apartment with separate kitchen, large living room, and three bedrooms. Building has elevator and storage unit included.
Ground floor studio apartment with direct access to communal garden. Perfect for plant lovers and those seeking outdoor space.
Modern apartment just 2 minutes from metro station. Open-plan living area, fitted kitchen, and bathroom with walk-in shower.
Top floor apartment with wraparound terrace. Floor-to-ceiling windows, luxury finishes, and smart home features throughout.
Family-friendly apartment in quiet residential area. Includes underground parking spot and storage room.
Compact studio apartment currently rented with stable tenant. Ideal investment opportunity in growing neighborhood.
Industrial-style loft with high ceilings and exposed brick walls. Custom-built mezzanine sleeping area.
Two-level apartment with spiral staircase. Upper floor features three bedrooms and bathroom, lower floor has living space and kitchen.
Perfect first apartment or student accommodation. Close to universities and public transport.
Bright apartment with south-facing balcony. Recently updated bathroom and kitchen appliances.
Corner apartment with dual aspect windows. Plenty of natural light and cross ventilation.
Efficiently designed studio in renovated historic building. Original features with modern amenities.
Large apartment suitable for extended family. Two bathrooms, separate kitchen, and multiple storage spaces.
Modern apartment with bonus room perfect for home office. Built-in storage throughout.
Central location with excellent amenities. Modern fixtures and fittings throughout.
Spacious apartment with river views. Three bedrooms, large living room, and modern kitchen.
Luxury apartment in new development. High-end finishes and smart home technology.
Ground floor apartment with small garden. Perfect for pet owners.
Compact living space with large separate storage room. Ideal for minimalist lifestyle.
Modern apartment complex with private garage space. Security system and reception.
Affordable starter apartment in good condition. Ready to move in.
